557
00:31:52.911 --> 00:31:54.545
Yeah. the ranch
is outside Lewiston.

558
00:31:54.612 --> 00:31:56.380
Near Roundup.
know where that is?

559
00:31:56.446 --> 00:31:57.548
I do.

560
