Excuse me. I'm sorry.

561
00:32:12.128 --> 00:32:14.331
Is he okay?

562
00:32:14.398 --> 00:32:17.601
He has Celiac Disease.

563
00:32:17.669 --> 00:32:19.704
He gets an upset tummy.

564
00:32:22.574 --> 00:32:24.241
He has what??

565
00:32:39.723 --> 00:32:42.593
[BREATHING DEEPLY]

566
00:32:56.340 --> 00:32:57.875
