- Daddy!

569
00:34:24.429 --> 00:34:27.898
We've checked every manifest
in every airstrip in the county.

570
00:34:27.965 --> 00:34:29.733
Sweetgrass. too...
nothing.

571
00:34:29.800 --> 00:34:33.037
He got that plane from
somewhere. you go find it.

572
00:34:33.103 --> 00:34:34.972
You'll be riding with
Agent Hendon Today.

573
00:34:35.039 --> 00:34:38.176
He knows the job.
Learn from him.

574
00:34:38.242 --> 00:34:39.344
You don't need
help around here?

575
00:34:39.411 --> 00:34:40.845
Just find the planes. son.

576
00:34:45.483 --> 00:34:48.385
Kayce.

577
00:34:48.452 --> 00:34:50.088
If you find anything.
don't confront anyone.

578
00:34:50.155 --> 00:34:51.889
You call the sheriff for backup.

579
00:34:51.956 --> 00:34:54.258
Everything by the book.

580
00:34:54.324 --> 00:34:55.592
I don't know the book.

581
00:34:55.659 --> 00:34:57.928
Well that's why you
call the sheriff. son.

582
00:34:57.996 --> 00:34:59.164
It's their book.

583
00:35:17.514 --> 00:35:18.649
When did all this burn?

584
00:35:18.715 --> 00:35:21.885
- Last year.
- Was it lightning?

585
00:35:21.952 --> 00:35:26.024
A satellite fell
out of the sky.

586
00:35:26.090 --> 00:35:28.159
God sure finds
interesting ways

587
00:35:28.226 --> 00:35:30.193
