588
00:35:30.260 --> 00:35:31.963
<i>108. there's
a depredation report.</i>

589
00:35:32.030 --> 00:35:34.798
<i>at the Paulson Ranch
near Ennis. Can we divert?</i>

590
00:35:34.865 --> 00:35:36.534
Copy that.

591
00:35:36.599 --> 00:35:38.068
It's on the way.
We're en route.

592
00:35:38.135 --> 00:35:39.704
We're supposed
to be checking airstrips

593
00:35:39.771 --> 00:35:41.239
