594
00:35:41.306 --> 00:35:43.675
We're checking airstrips
because of dead cows.

595
00:35:43.740 --> 00:35:46.478
Paulson's cows ain't
any less dead than yours.

596
00:35:53.418 --> 00:35:55.686
Put a wire in
to keep them from coming back

597
00:35:55.753 --> 00:35:57.956
